room_title: Escape room "Assassin's Deadly Game" by Hour to Midnight in Portland
room_description: You and your team have entered the FBI's cadet program, and your first task is to enter the safe-house of one of the greatest assassins to date. Your mission is to track down the assassin and help keep his next target alive. Can you save the day, or will you fall victim to the Assassin's Deadly Game?
